1
00:00:01,080 --> 00:00:03,520
It's been a while since I've been to school.

2
00:00:04,880 --> 00:00:05,880
Hey.

3
00:00:06,760 --> 00:00:08,840
Are you and Iijima Hinata close?

4
00:00:09,240 --> 00:00:10,240
Huh?

5
00:00:10,480 --> 00:00:11,480
Well, look.

6
00:00:11,720 --> 00:00:13,480
You two have been walking to school together a lot lately.

7
00:00:17,160 --> 00:00:18,240
Alright everyone,

8
00:00:18,240 --> 00:00:20,120
let's decide what we're doing for this year's school festival.

9
00:00:20,120 --> 00:00:21,680
Yeah!

10
00:00:21,680 --> 00:00:22,880
It's that time already?

11
00:00:24,160 --> 00:00:25,160
Any ideas?

12
00:00:25,680 --> 00:00:26,680
A cafe!

13
00:00:26,760 --> 00:00:27,760
A haunted house!

14
00:00:29,760 --> 00:00:31,000
A petting zoo!

15
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:32,920
How are we supposed to pull off a petting zoo?

16
00:00:34,760 --> 00:00:35,560
Oh!

17
00:00:35,560 --> 00:00:36,600
How about a play?

18
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:37,640
A play?

19
00:00:38,720 --> 00:00:39,800
Hey, that's not bad!

20
00:00:40,320 --> 00:00:41,160
I want to be in it!

21
00:00:41,160 --> 00:00:41,680
Really?

22
00:00:41,720 --> 00:00:44,240
Oh, that's a great idea!

23
00:00:45,480 --> 00:00:46,760
And look!

24
00:00:46,760 --> 00:00:47,920
Kono-kun is so handsome!

25
00:00:47,920 --> 00:00:49,040
Wouldn't he be perfect for the lead role?

26
00:00:50,240 --> 00:00:52,040
Exactly! I second that!

27
00:00:52,040 --> 00:00:52,720
Right?

28
00:00:52,720 --> 00:00:54,040
No... I...

29
00:00:54,560 --> 00:00:55,600
Come on, please!

30
00:00:56,560 --> 00:00:57,800
"Brother,"

31
00:00:58,200 --> 00:00:59,520
"You're so unfair!"

32
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:01,560
Alright! It's settled.

33
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:04,880
Kono Mizuki will star in our festival play!

34
00:01:05,160 --> 00:01:07,040
Yeah!

35
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:08,760
I want to play the lead actress!
